{"word":"G5111 - τολμάω - tolmáō - tol-mah'-o - Be bold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τολμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tolmáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tol-mah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be bold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துணிந்திரு. கண்டிப்பாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to dare"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;</b> <b>tolma</b> (<i>boldness</i>; probably itself from the base of <a href=\"#/G5056 - τέλος - télos - tel'-os/5056\">G5056</a> through the idea of <i>extreme</i> conduct); to <i>venture</i> (objectively or in <i>act</i>; while <a href=\"#/G2292 - θαῤῥέω - tharrhéō - thar-hreh'-o/2292\">G2292</a> is rather subjective or in <i>feeling</i>); by implication to be <i>courageous:</i> - be bold, boldly, dare, durst.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5111/5111\">G5111</a>, <a href=\"#/G5112/5112\">G5112</a>, <a href=\"#/G5113/5113\">G5113</a>, <a href=\"#/G662/662\">G662</a>"}]}